OL,3,CMedia mogul Jimmy Lai testifies in
OL,4,CHong Kong national security trial
OL,6,FJimmy Lai has told a court in Hong
OL,7,FKong that he hoped Donald Trump would
OL,8,Fstop the National Security Law being
OL,9,Fimposed by Beijing in 2020.
OL,11,FSpeaking in his defence for the first
OL,12,Ftime since he was jailed almost four
OL,13,Fyears ago, the 76-year-old explained
OL,14,Fhow he thought President Trump might
OL,15,Fhelp: "Maybe just ask China not to do
OL,16,Fit or whatever. A call to China, a
OL,17,Fcall to Xi Jinping, whatever."
