OL,3,CMedia mogul Jimmy Lai testifies in
OL,4,CHong Kong national security trial
OL,6,FThe former newspaper owner and
OL,7,Factivist is on trial for sedition and
OL,8,Fcollusion under Hong Kong's National
OL,9,FSecurity law which was introduced in
OL,10,FJune 2020. Following Jimmy Lai's
OL,11,Farrest his newspaper offices were
OL,12,Fraided, and his business was forced to
OL,13,Fclose.
OL,15,FHis trial started in December last
OL,16,Fyear but has been plagued by delays
OL,17,Fwhich his family say have compounded
OL,18,Fthe impact on his health.
