OL,3,CMedia mogul Jimmy Lai testifies in
OL,4,CHong Kong national security trial
OL,6,FIn his testimony, Lai stated that he
OL,7,Fhad never met Donald Trump in person
OL,8,Fduring his first presidency, but he
OL,9,Fdid travel to Washington in 2019 and
OL,10,Fmeet with Mike Pence and Mike Pompeo,
OL,11,Fthe then Vice President and Secretary
OL,12,Fof State respectively.
OL,14,FThe meetings were among several Lai
OL,15,Fheld with lawmakers during his visit
OL,16,Fto the US which he said was to tell
OL,17,Fthem about the pro-democracy protests
OL,18,Fwhich had gripped Hong Kong that year.
