OL,3,CMedia mogul Jimmy Lai testifies in
OL,4,CHong Kong national security trial
OL,6,FIt is alleged by the prosecution that
OL,7,FMr Lai used his contacts to try to
OL,8,Finfluence foreign policy on Hong Kong.
OL,9,FBeing led through a series of
OL,10,Fquestions by his defence lawyer Steven
OL,11,FKwan, Mr Lai said he had never donated
OL,12,Fany money to any political
OL,13,Forganisations or people outside of
OL,14,FHong Kong and he had never been a
OL,15,Fmember of any political party. He
OL,16,Fstated he had only ever donated money
OL,17,Fin the US "for think tanks and
OL,18,Freligious organisations".
