OL,9,Fnewspaper the Apple Daily and Next
OL,10,FMagazine.
OL,12,FHe replied that it appeared a good
OL,13,Fbusiness opportunity and "the more
OL,14,Finformation you have, the more you are
OL,15,Fin the know, the more you are free".
