OL,3,CMedia mogul Jimmy Lai testifies in
OL,4,CHong Kong national security trial
OL,6,FJimmy Lai started his newspaper in
OL,7,F1995 in the wake of the Tiananmen
OL,8,FSquare crackdown and just before Hong
OL,9,FKong's handover to China. For thirty
OL,10,Fyears he was one of the city's most
OL,11,Fprominent figures, joining many
OL,12,Fcampaigns for democracy and freedom of
OL,13,Fspeech. He had long been a target of
OL,14,Fthe Chinese Communist Party and was
OL,15,Fone of the first arrested under the
OL,16,FNational Security Law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
