OL,3,CMedia mogul Jimmy Lai testifies in
OL,4,CHong Kong national security trial
OL,6,FJimmy Lai has pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Ftwo conspiracy charges of collusion
OL,8,Fwith foreign forces and a third count
OL,9,Fof conspiracy to print and distribute
OL,10,Fseditious publications in his now-
OL,11,Fclosed Apple Daily tabloid newspaper.
OL,13,FHe is expected to remain on the
OL,14,Fwitness stand for fifteen days, before
OL,15,Fbeing cross-examined by the
OL,16,Fprosecution. If he is found guilty, he
OL,17,Fcould face a life sentence.
